org.ietf.nea.pt.socket.sasl

Class ExternalServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ietf.nea.pt.socket.sasl.ExternalServer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SaslServer

    public class ExternalServer
extends Object
implements SaslServer
    Implements the EXTERNAL SASL server-side mechanism. (RFC 2222). It processes an authorization callback for the requested authorization ID.
